com.aevi.magstripe

  • Packages that use com.aevi.magstripe 
    Package Description
    com.aevi.magstripe
    This package provides access to the magnetic stripe reader for non payment cards.
  • Classes in com.aevi.magstripe used by com.aevi.magstripe 
    Class and Description
    MagStripeTrack
    The MagStripeTrack contains the information found on one track of a mag stripe card.
    MagStripeTracks
    The MagStripeTrack contains the information found of a mag stripe card.
    OnSwipeCallback
    OnSwipeCallback is an interface that is used for creating a callback for use in the MagStripeService.swipe(OnSwipeCallback) method.
